org.sbml.jsbml.ext.render.director

Interface LayoutBuilder<P>

  • Type Parameters:
    P - Type of the product.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractLayoutBuilder

    public interface LayoutBuilder<P>
    LayoutBuilder provides methods to build graphical representations for all glyph types.
    Since:
    1.4
    Author:
    Mirjam Gutekunst
